# AI tooling — never committed.
#
# Excludes per-machine settings, project memories, caches, and
# rule files for every coding-assistant tool. Two concerns:
# (1) per-user / per-machine settings (allowlists, model
# preferences, auth state) leaking into the public repo, and
# (2) project-memory files containing internal context.
